This change:
1. Uses `\n` instead of ` | ` to separate different labels
2. Adds additional tick configuration to properly handle multiline labels:
   - `autoSkip: false` to prevent Chart.js from automatically skipping labels
   - `maxRotation: 0` and `minRotation: 0` to keep labels horizontal
   - `major.enabled: true` to ensure proper spacing for major ticks

This will display different labels vertically stacked instead of horizontally separated, making them easier to read when there are multiple values.
